becka(-at-)eastlink.ca wrote:

> I am trying to remember the floor jack jacking point.

I usually put the cup under the front tranny mount bolts.  That or on 
the side of the bus where the jacks go in.

> I am assuming the handles of the jackstands point towards the inside of the vehicle.

I put the jackstands just inside of the stock VW jacking points, the 
reinforced spot, where the chassis structures intersect.
